The paper discusses the construction of an experimental stand for cloud computing and network management in educational institutions. This involves dealing with security, processing speed, and other tasks, which are all related to networking and distributed systems (cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.Distributed). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of virtual laboratories, which is a software engineering concept (cs.SE). Finally, security is also mentioned, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
